summary: ConocoPhillips (NYSE:COP) recently appointed Ms. Kathleen McGinty to its board, enhancing focus on sustainability. The company experienced a 7.78% rise in share price over the last month, a period marked by the removal from two Russell indices, which may have slightly countered broader favorable market trends.
